
PROPOSED: http://jira.pcgen.org/browse/NEWTAG-331

NATURALWEAPON:A|B|C|D|E|F|A|B|C|D|E|F|Z

A= PRIMARY=WeaponName or
A= SECONDARY=WeaponName - designates whether an attack is Primary or Secondary and names it
B= Weapon Types
C= Number of Attacks
D= Damage
E= EXTRADAMAGE= (Optional)
F= SPROP= (Optional)
Z= PREXXX - only allowed at the very end of the complete tag

Example:

NATURALWEAPON:PRIMARY=Claw|Weapon.Natural.Weapon Group Natural|*2|1d6|EXTRADAMAGE=1d6|SPROP=Claws rend|SECONDARY=Bite|Weapon.Natural.Weapon Group Natural|*1|1d8|EXTRADAMAGE=1d8|SPROP=Bite hurts|PREFEAT:1,Uber Claws


